options.footer_text: Brought to you by D6-System, Got IT Systems and ValkyriaBot

options.field_value: First you need to setup your system and (if you want it) your fronter category.

To setup your system you use the command:
/setupsys xxxxxx
Replace the xxxxxx with your system ID.

To setup your fronter channel you use the command:
/setupfronter name
Replace name with the name for the channel category.

Want pingable roles for your alters?
Use /reloadalters

Beware, its going to take a while to create and refresh the roles. Please be patient.

Beware, DIscord has a max of 250 roles per server. If you have more members than that, it won't work.
